Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all! We are-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're releasing our debut single-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's ticking. This place isn't free, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think we should try finding a bassist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Would be nice if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think we're doing pretty well\Nwith just the three of us for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that girl talking just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No clue. Probably their new vocalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Never saw her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something about her catch your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...It can't be, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,RAISE YOUR VOICE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Momo-chan! How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, less than two probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see this place hasn't changed much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure it has, we're a hair away from going under here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, you were so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They just look alike...right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take a look inside if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much smaller than the stage we played on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to fit in here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Most live houses are about this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Though this one's been around for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so it has its regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And they won't go easy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss said he'd like us to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself if you're not feeling up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably practice some mo-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At least hesitate a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally hooked now...you'd never think\Nshe was freaking out so much last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're talking about a 20-minute performance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it shouldn't be that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And here are your tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you're not allowed to advertise me\N as a former Diamond Dust member, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a new band with these two, and-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd have to sell those ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}DID YOU SELL ANY?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THERE'S NO WAY I DID
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I ONLY HAVE TWO LEFT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}NO WAY!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TRY YOUR PREP SCHOOL, THERE'S GOTTA BE SOMEONE THERE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}IT'S NOT YOUR HOMETOWN, SO IT'S NOT LIKE ANYONE WILL RECOGNIZE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, I'm doing a concert with my band...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You...interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more into heavy metal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's totally cool, we're uhhh...\Nsort of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just gave it to her for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Customers over profits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we're doing this for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is to get lots of\Npeople to come, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a life lesson for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,People hate it when something they paid for goes to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it was something they got\Nfor free, they won't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, giving out tickets for free\Nmeans we're the ones paying for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-You really don't know anything, huh?\N-Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, {\il1}we're{\il0} the ones\N buying those tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We paid the live house for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The minimum amount of tickets you need\Nto sell is lower these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but in general, if you want to perform,\N you need to pay performing fees
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and for a minimum amount of tickets.\NThat way even if no one comes to your concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the live house is guaranteed at least the bare minimum profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how the business works!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you during your break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Momoka-san told us she was\Npaying for those tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're basically kids to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're younger, and we're not exactly\Nfunctioning members of society yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Momo-chan's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a new thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, where was it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to sell us tickets again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Dust, that band that's getting their big break now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they used to play here a lot.\NSo they paid a visit earlier and left these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're giving them to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They have this big agency backing them now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I kind of lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why Momoka-san left Diamond Dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but apparently the agency started making\Na lot of changes to the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Their look, songs and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She hated the idea and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a ticket for her too if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you gonna give it to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I feel like we'll get into a fight if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...I want to see them for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go together then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda curious myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the girl that gave me\Nconcert tickets before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have some left?\NThree of my friends want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 7500 yen in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, you were charging for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to buy if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just flip it on her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well what was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like "We were told to give them away at first so I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but then the live house suddenly changed their mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you're already a valuable customer,\NI'll cut you a deal -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Three for 2500 each instead of 3000 each. Sound good?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's called lying.\N - That's called working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Numbers 500 to 550, please enter the venue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A full house, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stationary at a crossroads\nthat doesn't appear on any map{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I rely on\nto find my way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's your own fault, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is so white\nEverything is so slow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the answers are\nvoid of substance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you {\i1}dare{\i0} sing that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait! It's barely been 5 minutes\nsince the concert started, what's gotten into-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Subaru-chan.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm this close to saying some\N{\i1}really{\i0} nasty things right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to let everything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}*indistinguishable gremlin noises*{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,JUST DIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understood that last part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, what is this, WHAT IS GOING ON??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just had to be Diamond Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The one thing that's as precious to me as my life. My treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to explain what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Their new singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to be friends, but not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nice to meet you all! We are-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Diamond Dust!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna break, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to listen to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You barge into their concert, get pissed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you're acting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what they call people like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Toxic fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly understand how I'm feeling right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, because I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that girl even become Diamond Dust's vocalist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That shallow little-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if she's there, it means she\N stood out enough to pass the auditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if she-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shut it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your problem, not theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it is, but I love and listen to Diamond Dust
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,more than anyone else in that audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly what makes you a toxic fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Dust doesn't exist just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about you,\Nare you really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be more popular than when I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're fine as long as they're popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than them not being popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always sticking your nose\Ninto other people's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said before, wasting time here\Nmeans wasting money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't practice with you two like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have steam to blow off,\Nbetter do it sooner than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,IZAKAYA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well?\N- Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, who comes to a bar\Nin their school uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm drinking alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always in your uniform anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Saves me the pain of choosing outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, high school girls get a lot of perks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, enough about me, have at it you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always sticking up for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sticking up for them or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you are. Think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the current Diamond Dust has nothing\Nto do with the Diamond Dust you were in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you defending them? It makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not involved with them anymore. They can do whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever path they choose,\NI don't have the right to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking for the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know how you actually feel about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was {\i1}your band.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The band you put your soul into.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just make your own assumptions about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Diamond Dust was
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,completely meaningless to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the new singer that's actually bothering you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking if you're really okay with the new Diamond Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry everyone, please don't pay us any mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, turn down the volume a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bands grow and change, just like people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an inevitable process.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You left because you didn't like\Nthat change you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they were becoming something\Ndifferent from the Diamond Dust you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were sure you weren't in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you hate what they're doing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the song I always listened to meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought that song was the heart and soul of DD.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just admit they changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That whatever {\i1}that{\i0} was\Nisn't the real Diamond Dust anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That they're-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved your Diamond Dust\Nmore than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is so white\NEverything is so slow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the answers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved your Diamond Dust\Nmore than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That song changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just abandon it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate it, and you still tell yourself that\Nyou're in the wrong and they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to lie to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the original\NDiamond Dust's dream was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To stay as a band together, with the\Noriginal members, until we were all wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To never quit no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it. None of us cared about music style\Nor anything like that at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grit your teeth for now."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Once we make it big, we'll be\Nable to play the way we want to."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They did everything they\Ncould to make me stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't work. I left them behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Oolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the commotion everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I love your music.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the original Diamond Dust is the\Nonly thing that touched my heart back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were the heart of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a mess of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be here if I wasn't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the drinks coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, wai-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, your face pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san, I thought you could hold your liquor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she did go at it pretty hard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She reeks of alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, you're dragging her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Subaru-chan, grab the legs!\N- Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's gonna work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san? We're going to\Nput you down for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was happy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be the one to\Nchoose our stage outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a friend you had a falling out with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,become the singer of your favorite group\Nisn't exactly a common experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You should make something out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting your anger, joy,\Nand sadness run free,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the great thing about being in a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The poster for our concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Featuring Momoka, former member of Diamond Dust"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, a good chunk of the people\Nthat went to DD's debut live
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will definitely come thanks to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to think about what kind of\Nimpact you'd want to make on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Outfits, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we have much money to spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we were thinking\Nwe'll have to make a big impact
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,at the next competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Momo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them not to write your name, but I guess\N the staff couldn't pass up the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, we got a full house thanks to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do we have our outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was thinking these would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make them together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're open to criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you'll still have to wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bare it all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be Momoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but girly music's not my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I shake the atmosphere up a bit before you're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really care...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about us, we'll shake it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka! We love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna start?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Impact...it's a nice word, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We struggle, we exhaust ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to stick it to someone, even\Nat the cost of getting hurt ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, your song...\Nit pierced through my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It had an impact on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if it was telling me,\N"Don't give up, even if you die trying".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make that impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream out everything you're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave nothing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let out all your frustrations, your shame,\Nyout anger, your sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,your pathetic self, that past you hate\Nso much you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,crawl into a bed and die, and all those regrets that haunt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay them all bare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}COWARD
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}DROPOUT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What we found\Nat this tumultuous crossroads{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hollow words\Nthat end up crumbling{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A shooting star could\Nsweep everything away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, nothing seems to change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We lie\Nto keep our hands clean{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our dreams falling apart in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We pretend nothing\Nwe hear nothing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch the storm pass by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The city is caught\Nin a whirlwind of truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where should we\Nlet ourselves be carried?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we can smile at the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}May our hands be tied{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we will only understand\nonce our dreams are abandoned{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our wishes are never heard{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a distorted world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can we do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can we improve?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you finally be discovered?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before everything collapses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's shape in the shadows{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The vision that drives us{\i0}
